<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Global Warming -->
  <GlobalWarming.label>气候变暖</GlobalWarming.label>
  <!-- EN: Global temperatures have suddenly risen to dangerous levels.\n\nFlora and Fauna is suffering from these changes as biomes shift into their warmer counterparts. Resources become scarce, forcing factions into conflict.\n\nIt will last anywhere between a season to several years. -->
  <GlobalWarming.description>全球气候剧变导致温度显著上升。动植物为适应炎热气候出现了不同幅度的转变，各地的生物群系也随之变化。资源变得稀缺，派系冲突加剧。这场全球范围的气候异常将持续至少一个季度，至多数年。</GlobalWarming.description>
  <!-- EN: The global warming is ending -->
  <GlobalWarming.endMessage>气候变暖结束了。</GlobalWarming.endMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: Ice Age -->
  <IceAge.label>冰河时代</IceAge.label>
  <!-- EN: Atmospheric composition of the planet drastically changed resulting in a significant drop in temperature.\n\nFlora and Fauna is suffering from these changes as biomes shift into their colder counterparts. Resources become scarce, forcing factions into conflict.\n\nIt will last anywhere between a season to several years. -->
  <IceAge.description>全球气候剧变导致温度显著下降。动植物为适应寒冷气候出现了不同幅度的转变，各地的生物群系也随之变化。资源变得稀缺，派系冲突加剧。这场全球范围的气候异常将持续至少一个季度，至多数年。</IceAge.description>
  <!-- EN: The ice age is ending -->
  <IceAge.endMessage>冰河时代结束了。</IceAge.endMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: Long Night -->
  <LongNight.label>无尽长夜</LongNight.label>
  <!-- EN: A space entity of unimaginable size has covered a local star, resulting in a long lasting eclipse.\n\nTerrified of this supernatural phenomenon, other factions will use this time to wage war and conflict across the surface.\n\nIt will last anywhere between a season to several years. -->
  <LongNight.description>一个庞大到难以想象的巨型太空实体遮住了恒星的光芒，引发了一场漫长的日食现象。资源变得稀缺，派系冲突加剧。这场全球范围的气候异常将持续至少一个季度，至多数年。</LongNight.description>
  <!-- EN: The long night is ending -->
  <LongNight.endMessage>长夜已尽，破晓降临。</LongNight.endMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: Psychic Bloom -->
  <PsychicBloom.label>灵爆</PsychicBloom.label>
  <!-- EN: A strong psychic pulse emitted by a long forgotten entity changed the very genetical structure of local flora. Whilst the sky filled with a seemingly endless auroras, colourful flowers started sprouting everywhere. \n\nAll pawns will gain a positive mood buff for the time of the event. The rapidly spreading flowers will overgrow everything, including your fields. \n\nIt will last anywhere between a few days to a season. -->
  <PsychicBloom.description>一个远古灵能实体放射出强大的灵能脉冲改变了当地植物群系的遗传结构。天空覆盖着无尽的极光，地上五颜六色的花朵四处绽放。所有的殖民者在此事件期间都会获得心情增益。迅速蔓延的花朵将会覆盖一切，包括你的田地。这场灵爆将持续至少几天，至多一个季度。</PsychicBloom.description>
  <!-- EN: The psychic bloom is ending -->
  <PsychicBloom.endMessage>灵爆结束了。</PsychicBloom.endMessage>
  
  <!-- EN: Psychic Rain -->
  <PsychicRain.label>灵能雾雨</PsychicRain.label>
  <!-- EN: A dangerous psychic entity caused disturbance on subatomic levels, resonating across all particles of the atmosphere.\n\nA seemingly endless supernatural rain has begun, altering the very composition of time. Any person or creature not under the roof will age significantly faster.\n\nIt will last anywhere between a season to several years. -->
  <PsychicRain.description>一个危险的灵能实体正在引发亚原子扰动，使大气层的粒子也产生共振。一场似乎永无尽头的超自然雾雨已经开始，时间结构被打乱。任何不在屋顶下的人类和动物都会加速衰老。这场全球范围的气候异常将持续至少一个季度，至多数年。</PsychicRain.description>
  <!-- EN: The psychic rain is ending -->
  <PsychicRain.endMessage>灵能雾雨结束了。</PsychicRain.endMessage>
  
</LanguageData>